<field_public_text>:
Enable BG bias current source (20 lines) from common block to the right hand side of TX/RX lane. Enable the desired current source from one common block only. If more than 1 common block are used and both enabled for this bit, bias current will be almost twice to the TX/RX lane which will cause function improperly.
